<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-16716] camel-mongodb streamFilter component option not honored</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-16716</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Although &lt;tt&gt;streamFilter&lt;/tt&gt; is declared as a &lt;tt&gt;UriParam&lt;/tt&gt;: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/main/components/camel-mongodb/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/mongodb/MongoDbEndpoint.java#L108&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/main/components/camel-mongodb/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/mongodb/MongoDbEndpoint.java#L108&lt;/a&gt; (it should be annotated as consumer only though)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;it is not honored. Such filter is only loaded from property: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/main/components/camel-mongodb/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/mongodb/MongoDbChangeStreamsConsumer.java#L60-L64&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/main/components/camel-mongodb/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/mongodb/MongoDbChangeStreamsConsumer.java#L60-L64&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;as reported in ckc issue: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel-kafka-connector/issues/1112&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel-kafka-connector/issues/1112&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
